sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as React Native UI
    participant AI as services/ai.ts
    participant AS as AsyncStorage
    participant EF as Supabase Edge Function<br/>(ai-breakdown)
    participant G as Gemini 2.0 Flash

    U->>UI: Taps "Break it down"
    UI->>AI: breakdownTask(title, subject, dueDate)
    AI->>AS: Check cache key:<br/>ai-breakdown-{title}-{dueDate}

    alt Cache Hit
        AS-->>AI: Return cached subtasks
        AI-->>UI: Return subtasks immediately
    else Cache Miss
        AI->>EF: POST /ai-breakdown<br/>{title, subject, dueDate}
        Note over EF: Build ADHD-aware prompt:<br/>• Deadline > 24h → first 3 subtasks ≤10min<br/>• Deadline ≤ 24h → ALL subtasks ≤10min<br/>• First subtask = concrete physical action<br/>• Max 8 subtasks total
        EF->>G: POST /generateContent<br/>with structured prompt
        G-->>EF: JSON response<br/>(possibly in markdown fences)
        Note over EF: Strip markdown fences<br/>Parse JSON<br/>Validate structure
        EF-->>AI: {subtasks: [...]}
        AI->>AS: Cache result
        AI-->>UI: Return subtasks
    end

    UI->>UI: Render StarterActionCard<br/>+ subtask checklist

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over AI,EF: Error Path
        EF--xAI: 500 / timeout / malformed
        AI-->>UI: FALLBACK_SUBTASKS<br/>(4 generic steps)
        UI->>UI: Show warm banner:<br/>"Using general steps"
    end
